1
00:00:00,930 --> 00:00:03,200
[After the date with Taichi]

2
00:00:13,570 --> 00:00:18,150
[Who is Min Seong waiting anxiously for?]

3
00:00:23,820 --> 00:00:28,090
[Lee Hyeong Jun: Hello.]
[Oh Min Seong: You're here.]

4
00:00:32,290 --> 00:00:37,230
[Oh Min Seong: What did you do before this?]
[Lee Hyeong Jun: I just had a chat at home.]

5
00:00:37,480 --> 00:00:40,020
[Oh Min Seong: With whom?]
[Lee Hyeong Jun: With everyone.]

6
00:00:40,020 --> 00:00:41,950
[Oh Min Seong: I see.]

7
00:00:47,090 --> 00:00:50,960
[Oh Min Seong: He had his bangs pulled back.
I thought it really suits him.]

8
00:00:50,960 --> 00:00:52,960
[Oh Min Seong: With his eyebrows showing,]

9
00:00:52,960 --> 00:00:56,840
[Oh Min Seong: he looks more manly
than his usual cute image.]

10
00:00:57,440 --> 00:00:59,440
[Oh Min Seong: It really suits him.]

11
00:01:00,840 --> 00:01:04,180
[Lee Hyeong Jun: I look very different
when I pull back my bangs.]

12
00:01:04,180 --> 00:01:07,580
[Lee Hyeong Jun: I wanted to
show him a different image.]

13
00:01:07,580 --> 00:01:10,920
[Lee Hyeong Jun: Min Seong said
he likes black the most,]

14
00:01:10,920 --> 00:01:16,120
[Lee Hyeong Jun: so after only wearing
bright colors, I dressed in black for the date.]

15
00:01:16,520 --> 00:01:21,130
[Oh Min Seong:
This date is only for 30 minutes.]

16
00:01:21,130 --> 00:01:24,130
[Lee Hyeong Jun: It's short.]

17
00:01:25,980 --> 00:01:27,700
[Hehe]

18
00:01:27,700 --> 00:01:31,000
[Lee Hyeong Jun: Why are you smiling?]
[Oh Min Seong: This hairstyle suits you.]

19
00:01:31,000 --> 00:01:32,140
[Lee Hyeong Jun: Really?]
[Oh Min Seong: Yeah.]

20
00:01:34,940 --> 00:01:38,680
[Lee Hyeong Jun: Are you still feeling unwell?]
[Oh Min Seong: It hurts so much. I'm dying.]

21
00:01:38,680 --> 00:01:40,610
[Lee Hyeong Jun:
And you're having a cold drink?]

22
00:01:40,610 --> 00:01:45,479
[Oh Min Seong: Are you worried about me?]
[Lee Hyeong Jun: I don't want to be infected.]

23
00:01:45,750 --> 00:01:51,090
[Oh Min Seong: You always say uncool things.
Just say you're worried about me.]

24
00:01:56,229 --> 00:02:00,630
[Oh Min Seong: This is the last date
before we make our final choice.]

25
00:02:00,630 --> 00:02:07,110
[Oh Min Seong: It's our last date.
So we should talk.]

26
00:02:07,710 --> 00:02:10,310
[Lee Hyeong Jun: Wow, it ends tomorrow.]
[Oh Min Seong: Yeah.]

27
00:02:10,310 --> 00:02:14,380
[Oh Min Seong: I'm just curious.]

28
00:02:14,380 --> 00:02:18,780
[Oh Min Seong: The way you think about me...]

29
00:02:19,150 --> 00:02:25,820
[Is it just for this show,
or will it extend beyond the show?]

30
00:02:26,320 --> 00:02:31,060
[Oh Min Seong: I want to talk about this.]

31
00:02:31,060 --> 00:02:35,270
[Oh Min Seong: You don't want to answer?]
[Lee Hyeong Jun: No, that's not it.]

32
00:02:35,270 --> 00:02:39,600
[Oh Min Seong: I came into this show]

33
00:02:39,600 --> 00:02:45,740
[Oh Min Seong: hoping for a relationship]

34
00:02:45,740 --> 00:02:50,480
[Oh Min Seong: that goes beyond the show.]

35
00:02:51,150 --> 00:02:55,750
[Oh Min Seong: Coming on this show,
I made my choices based on whether]

36
00:02:55,750 --> 00:02:58,820
[Oh Min Seong: we could
continue dating after the show.]

37
00:02:58,820 --> 00:03:05,500
[Oh Min Seong: So of course I chose someone
whom I want to continue seeing after the show.]

38
00:03:05,500 --> 00:03:07,100
[Oh Min Seong: If we are fond of each other,]

39
00:03:07,100 --> 00:03:10,500
[Oh Min Seong: I think
we can become a real couple.]

40
00:03:11,300 --> 00:03:13,370
[It's fate after all.]

41
00:03:15,310 --> 00:03:18,910
[Lee Hyeong Jun: I'm not good
at expressing myself in words,]

42
00:03:20,440 --> 00:03:27,190
[Lee Hyeong Jun: but I always chose you.
I called you too.]

43
00:03:32,190 --> 00:03:33,730
[Oh Min Seong: And?]

44
00:03:34,860 --> 00:03:37,130
[Lee Hyeong Jun: I'm shy.]

45
00:03:38,060 --> 00:03:45,870
[Lee Hyeong Jun: Anyway, if we become a couple,
the relationship will be public.]

46
00:03:46,200 --> 00:03:50,410
[Lee Hyeong Jun: I was
worried about those things.]

47
00:03:51,010 --> 00:03:56,880
[Lee Hyeong Jun: But I don't want to
worry about those things anymore.]

48
00:04:00,150 --> 00:04:04,690
[Lee Hyeong Jun: I did miss you today.]

49
00:04:05,920 --> 00:04:07,160
[Oh Min Seong: Really?]
[Lee Hyeong Jun: Yeah.]

50
00:04:07,160 --> 00:04:09,230
[Oh Min Seong: Today?]
[Lee Hyeong Jun: Yeah.]

51
00:04:09,230 --> 00:04:12,500
[Oh Min Seong: It's your first time missing me?]
[Lee Hyeong Jun: Well...]

52
00:04:13,500 --> 00:04:15,330
[Lee Hyeong Jun: I don't know.]

53
00:04:16,769 --> 00:04:21,610
[Oh Min Seong: So cold.
A cold and shrewd Seoulite.]

54
00:04:24,510 --> 00:04:28,510
[Lee Hyeong Jun: I've never been
good at expressing myself. I was shy too.]

55
00:04:28,510 --> 00:04:35,920
[Lee Hyeong Jun: I tried my best, though
it was indirect. I hope he saw my efforts.]

56
00:04:36,520 --> 00:04:40,020
[Oh Min Seong: It was cute. I liked it.]

57
00:04:41,860 --> 00:04:45,800
[Oh Min Seong: He's unfathomable.
Can't figure him out.]

58
00:04:46,130 --> 00:04:49,470
[Oh Min Seong: But he also knows how
to be cutesy and affectionate. It's cute.]

59
00:04:49,930 --> 00:04:54,010
[Oh Min Seong: So how should I interpret this?]
[Lee Hyeong Jun: What do you mean?]

60
00:04:54,010 --> 00:04:56,540
[Oh Min Seong: How should I interpret this?]

61
00:04:57,010 --> 00:05:00,410
[Lee Hyeong Jun: Do I have to spell it out?]

62
00:05:00,750 --> 00:05:02,210
[Oh Min Seong: I have no idea.]

63
00:05:02,210 --> 00:05:04,880
[Lee Hyeong Jun: You don't?]
[Oh Min Seong: You always have a poker face,]

64
00:05:04,880 --> 00:05:07,550
[Oh Min Seong: and you never say much.]

65
00:05:07,550 --> 00:05:09,500
[Oh Min Seong: Although I'm a shy person,]

66
00:05:09,500 --> 00:05:13,220
[Oh Min Seong: I'm like a clown in front of you.]
[Lee Hyeong Jun: I put in a lot of effort too.]

67
00:05:13,220 --> 00:05:16,430
[Oh Min Seong: I know.]
[Lee Hyeong Jun: I gave you the heart.]

68
00:05:16,430 --> 00:05:18,230
[Oh Min Seong: It's cute.]

69
00:05:18,560 --> 00:05:20,900
[Lee Hyeong Jun: It's cute, right?]
[Oh Min Seong: Yeah.]

70
00:05:21,300 --> 00:05:24,970
[Lee Hyeong Jun: I have one too.]
[Oh Min Seong: You're wearing it.]

71
00:05:24,970 --> 00:05:26,900
[Oh Min Seong:
I have both the star and the heart.]

72
00:05:26,900 --> 00:05:29,840
[Lee Hyeong Jun: I wanted to
give it to you at the end,]

73
00:05:30,170 --> 00:05:34,650
[Lee Hyeong Jun: but you said you were
going on a date with another person.]

74
00:05:34,650 --> 00:05:36,580
[Lee Hyeong Jun: So I got anxious.]

75
00:05:36,580 --> 00:05:43,050
[Oh Min Seong: That's why I'm wearing it.
So everyone can see it.]

76
00:05:43,450 --> 00:05:45,260
[Lee Hyeong Jun:
I kept mine hidden, though.]

77
00:05:45,320 --> 00:05:46,520
[Lee Hyeong Jun: It made me so happy.]

78
00:05:46,520 --> 00:05:52,260
[Lee Hyeong Jun: I was really happy that
he wore the keychain I gave him right away.]

79
00:05:52,330 --> 00:05:54,130
[Oh Min Seong: I like it.]

80
00:05:54,200 --> 00:05:57,670
[Oh Min Seong: In the morning, when I
told him I was gonna go on another date,]

81
00:05:57,670 --> 00:06:00,540
[Oh Min Seong: he gave me this.
That's cute of him too.]

82
00:06:04,140 --> 00:06:07,680
[Oh Min Seong: Why are you so quiet?]

83
00:06:07,680 --> 00:06:09,410
[Oh Min Seong: I like you
even if you don't say anything.]

84
00:06:09,410 --> 00:06:12,200
[Lee Hyeong Jun: I'm always quiet.
Didn't you know?]

85
00:06:12,200 --> 00:06:14,350
[Oh Min Seong: No, I knew.]

86
00:06:14,350 --> 00:06:17,620
[Oh Min Seong: But I still like you.]

87
00:06:17,620 --> 00:06:20,830
[Oh Min Seong: What'd it be like
seeing each other after this show?]

88
00:06:20,830 --> 00:06:23,430
[Oh Min Seong: I can't really imagine it.]

89
00:06:23,430 --> 00:06:27,170
[Oh Min Seong: On this show,
we're in a setting away from real life.]

90
00:06:27,170 --> 00:06:31,100
[Oh Min Seong: When we go back
to our daily lives and see each other...]

91
00:06:31,100 --> 00:06:35,170
[Lee Hyeong Jun: Wouldn't it be similar
to the date we had in Seoul?]

92
00:06:35,170 --> 00:06:37,180
[Oh Min Seong: I really enjoyed that date.]
[Lee Hyeong Jun: It was very comfortable.]

93
00:06:37,440 --> 00:06:39,909
[Oh Min Seong: I had a great time.]

94
00:06:40,240 --> 00:06:42,980
[Their Seoul date that was
blended into everyday living]

95
00:06:43,650 --> 00:06:48,050
[Moving forward, will they
be able to share their daily lives?]

96
00:06:50,320 --> 00:06:54,460
[Lee Hyeong Jun: Pour it for me.]
[Oh Min Seong: Don't you have hands?]

97
00:06:54,460 --> 00:06:57,060
[Lee Hyeong Jun: I like it
when people pour it for me.]

98
00:06:57,460 --> 00:07:00,400
[Oh Min Seong: What about me?]
[Lee Hyeong Jun: Hmm? Yours is full.]

99
00:07:00,400 --> 00:07:05,000
[Oh Min Seong: I'm asking if you like me.]
[Lee Hyeong Jun: You're not bad.]

100
00:07:05,000 --> 00:07:07,900
[Oh Min Seong: For goodness' sake!]

101
00:07:07,900 --> 00:07:09,800
[Oh Min Seong: Say if you like me or not.]

102
00:07:09,800 --> 00:07:12,810
[Lee Hyeong Jun: I like you.]

103
00:07:15,280 --> 00:07:17,420
[Oh Min Seong: You're really
bad at expressing yourself.]

104
00:07:17,420 --> 00:07:21,750
[Lee Hyeong Jun: Yeah I'm bad at it.]
[Oh Min Seong: You're really bad at it.]

105
00:07:22,020 --> 00:07:25,360
[Oh Min Seong: I'll accommodate it.
That's how you are, right?]

106
00:07:25,360 --> 00:07:27,230
[Lee Hyeong Jun: Yeah.]
[Oh Min Seong: Yeah, OK.]

107
00:07:27,830 --> 00:07:32,430
[Oh Min Seong: I'm happy to be with you.
That's all I need.]

108
00:07:32,430 --> 00:07:35,500
[Oh Min Seong: I feel relieved.]
[Lee Hyeong Jun: Why?]

109
00:07:35,500 --> 00:07:38,840
[Oh Min Seong: I just feel relieved.]

110
00:07:40,340 --> 00:07:45,340
[My worries have been resolved.]

111
00:07:45,940 --> 00:07:48,380
[Before they knew it, their feelings
for each other have gotten stronger]

112
00:07:48,650 --> 00:07:52,580
[Lee Hyeong Jun: I'm leaving.]
[Oh Min Seong: Bye. See you at home.]

113
00:07:52,580 --> 00:07:56,850
[Lee Hyeong Jun: Though it's a pity
the date was really short,]

114
00:07:56,850 --> 00:08:02,260
[Lee Hyeong Jun: I'm glad we could completely
clarify how we feel about each other.]

115
00:08:02,260 --> 00:08:06,060
[Oh Min Seong: When I first came here,
the first person I met]

116
00:08:06,060 --> 00:08:09,330
[Oh Min Seong: was Hyeong Jun.
From then on,]

117
00:08:09,330 --> 00:08:13,670
[Oh Min Seong: we spent every day together.]

118
00:08:16,070 --> 00:08:23,680
[Oh Min Seong: So, from then to now,
everyday with him felt like destiny.]

119
00:08:25,420 --> 00:08:30,150
[Love that came like destiny,
may it be forever]

120
00:08:31,090 --> 00:08:33,419
[Waiting for his next date]

121
00:08:38,760 --> 00:08:42,230
[Who is Su Min waiting for?]

122
00:08:50,470 --> 00:08:52,080
[Kim Sun Wook: Hello.]

123
00:08:52,080 --> 00:08:53,540
[Kim Su Min: Hi.]
[Kim Sun Wook: Hi.]

124
00:08:54,210 --> 00:08:57,550
[Kim Su Min: We meet often.]
[Kim Sun Wook: I know.]

125
00:08:57,610 --> 00:09:02,420
[Kim Su Min: Our eyes met
when he walked in. He was all smiles,]

126
00:09:02,420 --> 00:09:04,420
[Kim Su Min: waving the camera at me.]

127
00:09:04,420 --> 00:09:08,890
[Kim Su Min: So he knew it was me
and brought it.]

128
00:09:09,540 --> 00:09:13,950
[Kim Sun Wook: I expected to see him.
So I was relaxed when I went on the date.]

129
00:09:14,280 --> 00:09:17,080
[Kim Sun Wook: I thought it was
the last time we could talk alone]

130
00:09:17,080 --> 00:09:18,690
[Kim Sun Wook: on this show,]

131
00:09:18,690 --> 00:09:21,690
[Kim Sun Wook: so I went on the date
without any worries.]

132
00:09:23,220 --> 00:09:24,690
[Kim Sun Wook: It's good to see you often.]

133
00:09:24,690 --> 00:09:26,160
[Kim Su Min: It's good?]
[Kim Sun Wook: Yeah.]

134
00:09:26,160 --> 00:09:28,900
[Kim Su Min: That's good.
Did you take a lot of photos?]

135
00:09:28,900 --> 00:09:30,700
[Kim Sun Wook: No,
I haven't taken any since then.]

136
00:09:30,700 --> 00:09:33,900
[Kim Su Min: What a pity.]

137
00:09:33,900 --> 00:09:35,500
[Kim Su Min: It's the last day.]

138
00:09:36,570 --> 00:09:40,840
[Kim Sun Wook: We're having
the last date together on the last day.]

139
00:09:42,380 --> 00:09:44,040
[Kim Su Min: Did you go on a date just now?]
[Kim Sun Wook: No, no.]

140
00:09:44,040 --> 00:09:45,650
[Kim Su Min: No?]
[Kim Sun Wook: Yeah.]

141
00:09:45,650 --> 00:09:48,050
[Kim Sun Wook: This is my first date today.]

142
00:09:49,980 --> 00:09:53,050
[Kim Su Min: It's my honor.]
[Kim Sun Wook: No, no.]

143
00:09:53,050 --> 00:09:57,300
[Kim Sun Wook: It's nice to
have a peaceful date like this.]

144
00:09:57,300 --> 00:09:58,730
[Kim Su Min: You're right.]

145
00:09:59,130 --> 00:10:01,600
[Kim Sun Wook:
Such a date has its advantages too.]

146
00:10:01,600 --> 00:10:04,260
[Kim Su Min: How was the week?]
[Kim Sun Wook: The week?]

147
00:10:05,470 --> 00:10:10,340
[Kim Sun Wook: I really enjoyed it.]
During the last shoot,]

148
00:10:10,600 --> 00:10:13,740
[Kim Sun Wook: it was
getting to know strangers.]

149
00:10:13,740 --> 00:10:18,210
[Kim Sun Wook: This time, I got to
know everyone on a deeper level.]

150
00:10:18,210 --> 00:10:21,680
[Kim Sun Wook: So I enjoyed it more.]

151
00:10:22,020 --> 00:10:24,950
[Kim Sun Wook: What about you?]

152
00:10:25,120 --> 00:10:31,860
[Kim Su Min: I've been... ah,
feeling all sorts of emotions.]

153
00:10:32,230 --> 00:10:34,760
[Kim Su Min: Right now too.]

154
00:10:34,760 --> 00:10:37,100
[Kim Su Min: I realized I'm really bad at]

155
00:10:37,100 --> 00:10:41,300
[Kim Su Min: expressing myself
to the one I like.]

156
00:10:41,300 --> 00:10:45,510
[Kim Sun Wook: In the past? Or now?]
[Kim Su Min: I still feel that way.]

157
00:10:45,770 --> 00:10:48,110
[Kim Sun Wook: It doesn't apply now.]
[Kim Su Min: Really?]

158
00:10:48,110 --> 00:10:49,780
[Kim Sun Wook: Yeah,
you've been really cool.]

159
00:10:52,380 --> 00:10:55,180
[Kim Su Min: On one hand, I still have regrets.]
[Kim Sun Wook: Why?]

160
00:10:55,180 --> 00:11:00,120
[Kim Su Min: I thought
I could've been more proactive.]

161
00:11:01,390 --> 00:11:05,860
[Kim Su Min: Other than
talking to you alone like this,]

162
00:11:05,860 --> 00:11:12,130
[Kim Su Min: I always felt
shy and nervous for no reason,]

163
00:11:12,130 --> 00:11:14,870
[Kim Su Min: and stopped myself
from making moves.]

164
00:11:16,600 --> 00:11:18,210
[Kim Su Min: So, a part of me]

165
00:11:18,210 --> 00:11:23,940
[Kim Su Min: still wishes
I were a bit more courageous.]

166
00:11:24,540 --> 00:11:29,420
[Kim Sun Wook: That's possible.
But I really felt your sincerity.]

167
00:11:29,820 --> 00:11:34,150
[Kim Sun Wook: You should not have regrets.
As the one on the receiving end,]

168
00:11:34,690 --> 00:11:39,630
[Kim Sun Wook: I completely felt your effort.
And I'm very grateful for it.]

169
00:11:40,230 --> 00:11:43,960
[Kim Sun Wook: I don't think
you should have any regrets.]

170
00:11:44,700 --> 00:11:48,640
[Kim Sun Wook:
I felt your efforts as they were.]

171
00:11:49,300 --> 00:11:52,170
[Kim Su Min: I was a little jealous.]

172
00:11:53,510 --> 00:11:57,510
[Kim Su Min: I did get a bit jealous.]
[Kim Sun Wook: That's human nature.]

173
00:11:55,900 --> 00:11:56,620
Right?

174
00:11:57,980 --> 00:12:00,850
[Kim Sun Wook: I really enjoyed
all the time I spent with you.]

175
00:12:03,920 --> 00:12:08,990
[Kim Su Min: When we're talking alone,
I have no problem looking into your eyes.]

176
00:12:08,990 --> 00:12:13,190
[Kim Su Min: But for some reason,
it's hard when we're in the rooms.]

177
00:12:13,190 --> 00:12:14,590
[Kim Sun Wook: Really?]

178
00:12:14,930 --> 00:12:18,330
[Kim Sun Wook: Why?]
[Kim Su Min: That's how I felt.]

179
00:12:18,730 --> 00:12:20,730
[Kim Su Min: Before you came in,]

180
00:12:20,730 --> 00:12:27,070
[Kim Su Min: I thought that since
we've talked a lot and had a date yesterday,]

181
00:12:27,070 --> 00:12:30,940
[Kim Su Min: I could treat this casually.
But somehow I got nervous again.]

182
00:12:31,340 --> 00:12:35,140
[Kim Sun Wook: The last date
is always like this.]

183
00:12:35,140 --> 00:12:36,950
[Kim Su Min: I got nervous for no reason.]

184
00:12:45,430 --> 00:12:49,030
[Kim Su Min: Want me to take photos for you?]
[Kim Sun Wook: So suddenly?]

185
00:12:49,030 --> 00:12:50,100
[Kim Sun Wook: All of a sudden?]

186
00:12:50,500 --> 00:12:52,830
[Kim Sun Wook: Let's do it together after.]
[Kim Su Min: OK.]

187
00:12:53,370 --> 00:12:56,640
[Kim Su Min: I hope you'll use up the film roll.]
[Kim Sun Wook: I think I will.]

188
00:13:01,440 --> 00:13:05,650
[Kim Su Min: I hope you can
take photos with everyone today.]

189
00:13:08,250 --> 00:13:10,780
[Kim Su Min: Still, I'm very happy
to talk to you like this]

190
00:13:10,780 --> 00:13:14,790
[Kim Su Min: for the last time.]
[Kim Sun Wook: It's not the last time.]

191
00:13:15,120 --> 00:13:21,460
[Kim Sun Wook: But like this... Anyway,
it may be the last time of significance]

192
00:13:21,460 --> 00:13:24,400
[Kim Sun Wook: on this show.]
[Kim Su Min: Yeah.]

193
00:13:24,400 --> 00:13:28,000
[Kim Sun Wook: For the two of us
to spare the time to do this.]

194
00:13:29,600 --> 00:13:32,740
[Kim Sun Wook: But I'm
always grateful to you]

195
00:13:32,740 --> 00:13:36,280
[Kim Sun Wook: for always
thinking of me in a positive light.]

196
00:13:36,280 --> 00:13:41,010
[Kim Sun Wook: If I were you,
I'd probably have some negative thoughts.]

197
00:13:41,010 --> 00:13:45,820
[Kim Sun Wook: But you didn't. You always
thought highly of me and took good care of me.]

198
00:13:45,820 --> 00:13:48,690
[Kim Sun Wook: I'm very grateful.]

199
00:13:48,960 --> 00:13:53,560
[Kim Su Min: There was someone else
I was a little curious about,]

200
00:13:53,560 --> 00:13:55,430
[Kim Su Min: but I couldn't help]

201
00:13:55,430 --> 00:14:00,370
[Kim Su Min: that my mind always
ended up landing on you.]

202
00:14:03,040 --> 00:14:08,240
[Kim Su Min: Even when I got
curious about that other person,]

203
00:14:08,240 --> 00:14:11,850
[Kim Su Min: the curiosity died out quickly.]

204
00:14:11,850 --> 00:14:16,180
[Kim Sun Wook: I must be very charming.]
[Kim Su Min: Immensely.]

