[Kim Han Gyeol: You actually believed him?]

421
00:28:06,810 --> 00:28:08,280
[Cho Yun Jae: Yes, I did.]

422
00:28:08,280 --> 00:28:11,820
[Eum Hyeok Jin: You must have chosen someone.
