429
00:28:27,260 --> 00:28:28,820
You're not young anymore.

430
00:28:29,420 --> 00:28:32,020
-I saw these yesterday. -Wearing these shoes.

431
00:28:38,240 --> 00:28:44,720
[Kim Han Gyeol: I was calming myself down
