434
00:28:49,260 --> 00:28:51,460
[Kim Sun Wook: I told him
not to hold his hands.]

435
00:28:50,660 --> 00:28:51,460
What?

436
00:28:51,460 --> 00:28:54,180
[Kim Sun Wook: I told him not to hold his hands.]
