[Lee Hyeong Jun: What? Why?]

441
00:29:03,070 --> 00:29:05,400
[Lee Hyeong Jun: Why hold hands?]
[Kim Sun Wook: I don't know.]

442
00:29:05,400 --> 00:29:07,120
