445
00:29:14,580 --> 00:29:15,820
[Lee Hyeong Jun: So you got jealous?]

446
00:29:15,820 --> 00:29:17,080
[Kim Sun Wook:
So I said I get jealous easily.]

447
00:29:17,080 --> 00:29:19,550
[Lee Hyeong Jun: Of course you got jealous.
