456
00:29:43,980 --> 00:29:46,310
[Kim Sun Wook: That's what I thought.]
[Eum Hyeok Jin: But it still bugged you.]

457
00:29:46,310 --> 00:29:47,600
[Kim Sun Wook: Yeah, so I thought]

458
00:29:47,600 --> 00:29:49,720
[Kim Sun Wook: I should tell him how I feel.]
[Eum Hyeok Jin: That's right.]

459
00:29:49,720 --> 00:29:51,520
[Kim Sun Wook: I have to make it clear.]

460
00:29:51,520 --> 00:29:54,590
[Kim Sun Wook: Yeah. So I told him.]

461
