[There's another man
who's finding it hard to make a choice]

1198
01:22:17,730 --> 01:22:22,570
[Who is Yun Jae's final choice?]

1199
01:22:32,940 --> 01:22:34,540
When did you get here?

1200
01:22:34,810 --> 01:22:39,620
[Since the first time they met,
Hyun Jun left a deep impression on him]

1201
01:22:35,460 --> 01:22:36,940
-Here? -Yes.

1202
01:22:36,940 --> 01:22:38,020
Since I've been here?

1203
01:22:38,020 --> 01:22:39,300
I don't know.

1204
01:22:39,860 --> 01:22:43,820
[Cho Yun Jae: What do you think I should do
to get Hyun Jun's attention?]

1205
01:22:44,700 --> 01:22:47,660
I think he's quite slow.

1206
01:22:44,820 --> 01:22:51,060
[He has a lot on his mind about Hyun Jun]

1207
01:22:47,940 --> 01:22:49,580
No. He reads the room quickly.

1208
01:22:49,580 --> 01:22:50,780
-Hyun Jun? -Yes.

1209
01:22:51,460 --> 01:22:53,590
He's actually observing everything.

1210
01:22:55,430 --> 01:22:59,100
[And for Hyun Jun,
he tried to muster up his courage]

1211
01:22:59,440 --> 01:23:02,840
["Hold my hand."]

1212
01:23:07,710 --> 01:23:09,380
[Cho Yun Jae: It's been so tiring.]

1213
01:23:09,380 --> 01:23:11,710
[Cho Yun Jae: Actually, I'm really tired.]

1214
01:23:11,700 --> 01:23:12,500
I don't know.

1215
01:23:14,120 --> 01:23:17,120
[Cho Yun Jae: I don't know. Anyway,]

1216
01:23:17,490 --> 01:23:22,960
["I think I still like you the most.
Even though I said those things."]

1217
01:23:24,700 --> 01:23:27,180
I don't know what I was thinking.

1218
01:23:24,760 --> 01:23:29,300
[In the end,
Hyun Jun didn't understand his feelings]

1219
01:23:30,330 --> 01:23:34,400
[To him, love is a wall
that can't be crossed]

1220
01:23:35,340 --> 01:23:38,470
[Will Yun Jae muster up his courage again
and fight for Hyun Jun?]

1221
01:23:51,890 --> 01:23:54,960
[Taichi: I didn't choose anyone in the final selection.]

1222
01:23:54,960 --> 01:23:58,090
[Taichi: In Men's House, I wasn't really]

1223
01:23:58,090 --> 01:24:01,160
[Taichi: romantically interested in anyone here.]

1224
01:24:01,560 --> 01:24:05,170
[He put his love diary
into the nameless mailbox]

1225
01:24:05,170 --> 01:24:08,640
[Taichi: I came to this show to find someone to date,]

1226
01:24:08,640 --> 01:24:10,170
[Taichi: yet I made this choice.]

1227
01:24:10,170 --> 01:24:12,780
[Taichi: It's a pity, but]

1228
01:24:12,780 --> 01:24:17,450
[Taichi: I made this choice which is true to my heart.]

1229
01:24:18,380 --> 01:24:21,720
[Q. Do you feel any regret
for your final choice?]

1230
01:24:21,720 --> 01:24:22,850
[Taichi: Of course, it was a pity.]

1231
01:24:22,850 --> 01:24:26,390
[Taichi: I came on this show to find a real partner.]

1232
01:24:26,390 --> 01:24:29,730
[Taichi: To get this result, it's quite a pity, but]

1233
01:24:29,730 --> 01:24:33,130
[Taichi: I tried my best. So I want to tell myself I did well]

1234
01:24:33,130 --> 01:24:35,660
[Taichi: and that I did well.]

1235
01:24:35,660 --> 01:24:38,530
[Taichi: At the same time it's quite a pity. I felt fifty-fifty in that sense.]

1236
01:24:38,930 --> 01:24:41,070
[Taichi: But I was really determined]

1237
01:24:41,070 --> 01:24:45,670
[Taichi: to not leave alone.]

1238
01:24:46,540 --> 01:24:49,950
[Another man
has given up his final choice]

1239
01:25:07,500 --> 01:25:12,300
[He put his 7 days of sincerity
into the nameless mailbox]

1240
01:25:17,440 --> 01:25:21,640
[Cho Yun Jae: I can guess the result.]

1241
01:25:21,640 --> 01:25:26,720
[Cho Yun Jae: The person I am interested in was very obvious about it.]

1242
01:25:26,720 --> 01:25:31,520
[Cho Yun Jae: When he feels burdened, he'd take the initiative to move away.]

1243
01:25:31,520 --> 01:25:37,730
[Cho Yun Jae: He probably wanted to draw a clear line.]

1244
01:25:37,730 --> 01:25:41,000
[Cho Yun Jae: And I also know that
Hyun Jun wouldn't choose me.]

1245
01:25:41,000 --> 01:25:45,670
[Cho Yun Jae: In any way, I might put him in a tight spot.]

1246
01:25:45,670 --> 01:25:52,410
[Cho Yun Jae: Hyun Jun and Sun Wook took the initiative
to come and talk to me.]

1247
01:25:52,410 --> 01:25:56,310
[Cho Yun Jae: Seeing them trying so hard,]

1248
01:25:56,310 --> 01:26:05,850
[Cho Yun Jae: I think I've met very nice people.]

1249
01:26:06,660 --> 01:26:11,260
[Cho Yun Jae: I'm most grateful to Sun Wook,
and I feel sorry too.]

1250
01:26:11,700 --> 01:26:14,100
[Cho Yun Jae: With Hyun Jun...]

1251
01:26:14,000 --> 01:26:16,420
With Hyun Jun.

1252
01:26:16,820 --> 01:26:17,860
Yes.

1253
01:26:19,600 --> 01:26:24,210
[Short but passionate heart flutters]

1254
01:26:22,260 --> 01:26:23,820
I think this is when his heart flutters the most.

1255
01:26:23,820 --> 01:26:24,540
This.

1256
01:26:31,280 --> 01:26:35,220
[Putting all the moments into his memories
and saying goodbye...]

1257
01:26:47,300 --> 01:26:52,630
[Sun Wook comes to the final choice place]

1258
01:26:55,240 --> 01:26:59,970
[Who's the man walking to Sun Wook?]

1259
01:27:08,780 --> 01:27:15,720
[Su Min chose Sun Wook]

1260
01:27:15,720 --> 01:27:17,930
[Kim Su Min: I really want to cheer for him.]

1261
01:27:18,460 --> 01:27:24,330
[Kim Su Min: Because I still like him.
So I think I should choose him]

1262
01:27:24,330 --> 01:27:26,600
[Kim Su Min: with my feelings.]

1263
01:27:26,600 --> 01:27:29,810
[Kim Su Min: So I chose him in the end.]

1264
01:27:29,820 --> 01:27:35,780
[Kim Sun Wook]

1265
01:27:35,780 --> 01:27:39,410
[Kim Su Min: I kept smiling awkwardly.]

1266
01:27:39,410 --> 01:27:41,680
[Kim Su Min: I felt lost.]

1267
01:27:42,350 --> 01:27:47,160
[Kim Su Min: Seeing him smiling in front of me made me very happy.]

1268
01:27:56,900 --> 01:27:58,900
[Kim Sun Wook: Hello?]

1269
01:27:58,900 --> 01:28:01,640
[Kim Su Min: I had a lot of fun these days.]

1270
01:28:04,370 --> 01:28:09,040
[Kim Sun Wook: Me too. Thanks to you.]

1271
01:28:12,650 --> 01:28:15,180
[Kim Su Min: Yes, you look so happy.]

1272
01:28:16,120 --> 01:28:19,990
[Kim Sun Wook: Seeing you here, I'm surprised.]

1273
01:28:21,120 --> 01:28:23,860
[Kim Sun Wook: Because of you, I had a lot of fun.]

1274
01:28:25,690 --> 01:28:29,060
["Yes, be happy..."]

1275
01:28:30,380 --> 01:28:31,970
[Kim Sun Wook: Okay.]

1276
01:28:34,200 --> 01:28:37,070
[Kim Su Min: I think we should follow our hearts.]

1277
01:28:37,070 --> 01:28:40,140
[Kim Su Min: So I called you.]
[Kim Sun Wook: I see.]

1278
01:28:40,540 --> 01:28:44,610
["I'm going to keep
showing my interest in you..."]

1279
01:28:44,980 --> 01:28:50,550
["Will he get hurt?
I was worried about that."]

1280
01:28:51,620 --> 01:28:54,020
["Let's go on a date."]

1281
01:28:54,020 --> 01:28:56,960
[Kim Sun Wook: A proper date?]

1282
01:28:57,360 --> 01:29:01,960
[Kim Su Min: I want you to be happy no matter what.]

1283
01:29:05,830 --> 01:29:08,840
[Kim Sun Wook: I'm happy now.]

1284
01:29:08,840 --> 01:29:12,510
[Kim Su Min: Shall we take some photos?]
[Kim Sun Wook: Shall we?]

1285
01:29:12,510 --> 01:29:14,580
[Kim Su Min: I'll take one for you.]

1286
01:29:15,210 --> 01:29:17,910
[Su Min hopes that Sun Wook
will always be happy]

1287
01:29:17,540 --> 01:29:18,140
Like this? Like this?

1288
01:29:18,140 --> 01:29:21,270
-A little to the front. -Like this? Like this? Like this?

1289
01:29:22,320 --> 01:29:28,520
[Kim Su Min: Bye.]
[Kim Sun Wook: Bye.]

1290
01:29:29,990 --> 01:29:32,590
[Su Min leaves no regrets whether coming to
show his love or turning to leave]

1291
01:29:32,590 --> 01:29:35,660
[Kim Su Min: I feel relieved now.]

1292
01:29:35,660 --> 01:29:40,000
[Kim Su Min: Because this was a big challenge in my life.]

1293
01:29:40,000 --> 01:29:42,670
[Kim Su Min: I made many attempts.]

1294
01:29:43,270 --> 01:29:46,410
[Kim Su Min: It was a period of time]

1295
01:29:46,410 --> 01:29:48,610
[Kim Su Min: where I could get by with more courage.]

1296
01:29:49,280 --> 01:29:50,950
[Kim Su Min: I feel great.]

1297
01:29:50,950 --> 01:29:56,490
[Kim Su Min: I think I've done something. So I'm proud of myself.]

1298
01:30:10,570 --> 01:30:13,700
[Kim Sun Wook: First of all, when I was waiting alone,]

1299
01:30:14,970 --> 01:30:18,910
[Kim Sun Wook: I was sure he'd come.]

1300
01:30:19,370 --> 01:30:22,240
[Waiting with confidence]

1301
01:30:28,650 --> 01:30:33,320
[Hyun Jun showed up as Sun Wook believed]

1302
01:30:40,260 --> 01:30:43,270
[Kim Sun Wook: He walked with big strides from afar.]

1303
01:30:43,270 --> 01:30:46,670
[Kim Sun Wook: My heart fluttered and I was happy.]

1304
01:30:54,410 --> 01:30:56,810
[Lee Hyun Jun: Hello.]
[Kim Sun Wook: Hello.]

1305
01:31:01,020 --> 01:31:03,490
[Lee Hyun Jun: Do I still look funny?]
[Kim Sun Wook: A little?]

1306
01:31:03,490 --> 01:31:05,550
[Lee Hyun Jun: Me?]
[Kim Sun Wook: A little.]

1307
01:31:08,090 --> 01:31:09,690
[Kim Sun Wook: Hello.]

1308
01:31:09,690 --> 01:31:12,490
[Lee Hyun Jun: Did you wait long?]
[Kim Sun Wook: A little.]

1309
01:31:17,300 --> 01:31:22,240
[Kim Sun Wook: I chose you in the final choice.]

1310
01:31:24,170 --> 01:31:28,380
[Lee Hyun Jun]
[Chose Hyun Jun with no doubt]

1311
01:31:28,380 --> 01:31:31,710
[Kim Sun Wook: I chose Hyun Jun. Because]

1312
01:31:31,710 --> 01:31:35,720
[Kim Sun Wook: as soon as I came here,
I was interested in him.]

1313
01:31:35,720 --> 01:31:38,590
[Kim Sun Wook: That's how it was from the beginning.
Then, the more I know him,]

1314
01:31:38,590 --> 01:31:41,920
[Kim Sun Wook: the more I think he is a good person.]

1315
01:31:41,920 --> 01:31:43,660
[Kim Sun Wook: And I like people who are shy]

1316
01:31:43,660 --> 01:31:45,990
[Kim Sun Wook: and reserved.]

1317
01:31:45,990 --> 01:31:49,000
[Kim Sun Wook: Because most of them]

1318
01:31:49,000 --> 01:31:52,470
[Kim Sun Wook: are actually filled with emotions on the inside.]

1319
01:31:52,470 --> 01:31:54,940
[Kim Sun Wook: I prefer this kind of people.]

1320
01:31:55,870 --> 01:31:58,670
[Kim Sun Wook: That's why he's attracted me more.]

1321
01:32:01,010 --> 01:32:03,680
[Lee Hyun Jun: I chose you too.]

1322
01:32:09,220 --> 01:32:11,820
[His interest leaned towards Sun Wook
bit by bit]

1323
01:32:13,420 --> 01:32:16,760
[Lee Hyun Jun: I chose Sun Wook because]

1324
01:32:16,760 --> 01:32:18,960
[Lee Hyun Jun: we've confirmed each other's feelings.]

1325
01:32:18,960 --> 01:32:23,030
[Lee Hyun Jun: Right from the start,
he's also showed a lot of interest in me.]

1326
01:32:23,030 --> 01:32:24,500
[Lee Hyun Jun: He cared for me too.]

1327
01:32:24,500 --> 01:32:27,440
[Lee Hyun Jun: That's why I chose him.]

1328
01:32:33,840 --> 01:32:38,080
[Lee Hyun Jun: What's wrong? Do I look like a robot again?]
[Kim Sun Wook: No, I'm just happy.]

1329
01:32:42,250 --> 01:32:44,990
["I like you a lot."]

1330
01:32:45,120 --> 01:32:48,590
[Lee Hyun Jun: Thank you for liking me.]
[Kim Sun Wook: Hey, what's with that reply?]

1331
01:32:48,590 --> 01:32:50,460
[Lee Hyun Jun: Am I wrong?]
[Kim Sun Wook: You're doing this again.]

1332
01:32:50,460 --> 01:32:52,790
[Lee Hyun Jun: Am I wrong?]
[Kim Sun Wook: At times like this...]

1333
01:32:52,790 --> 01:32:55,800
[Lee Hyun Jun: How about times like this?]

1334
01:32:56,200 --> 01:33:00,400
[Kim Sun Wook: I got it. Thank god.]

1335
01:33:00,870 --> 01:33:06,410
[Lee Hyun Jun: Why are you laughing like that?]
[Kim Sun Wook: I'm laughing because I'm happy.]

1336
01:33:07,340 --> 01:33:12,810
[Lee Hyun Jun: Thank you.]
[Kim Sun Wook: Thank you, too.]

1337
01:33:12,810 --> 01:33:16,220
[Kim Sun Wook: I can feel it all.
Though you put it this way in words.]

1338
01:33:17,290 --> 01:33:19,760
[Lee Hyun Jun: I'm glad you can feel it.]

1339
01:33:19,760 --> 01:33:23,560
[Kim Sun Wook: But I have something for you.]
[Lee Hyun Jun: What is it?]

1340
01:33:29,630 --> 01:33:33,300
[Lee Hyun Jun: "Hyun Jun, I like you a lot"?]

1341
01:33:33,740 --> 01:33:37,700
[12/9—Hyun Jun, I like you a lot.
-Sun Wook]

1342
01:33:44,250 --> 01:33:49,780
[How Hyun Jun acts when he gets bolder]

1343
01:33:53,520 --> 01:33:56,730
["I like you too."]

1344
01:33:56,790 --> 01:33:59,390
[Lee Hyun Jun: My heart fluttered and I was really happy.]

1345
01:33:59,390 --> 01:34:02,660
[Lee Hyun Jun: He was standing above looking at me.
He's so small and he's so cute.]

1346
01:34:02,660 --> 01:34:05,800
[Kim Sun Wook: My heart fluttered, of course. That he did that in the open.]

1347
01:34:05,800 --> 01:34:08,940
[Kim Sun Wook: I thought, "Oh, he's mustered up some courage,"
and thought that's cute.]

1348
01:34:09,810 --> 01:34:10,870
[Lee Hyun Jun: It's cold. Let's go in.]

1349
01:34:10,870 --> 01:34:11,410
[Kim Sun Wook: Let's go.]

1350
01:34:20,420 --> 01:34:23,080
[Lee Hyun Jun: Yes, I was happy.]

1351
01:34:23,080 --> 01:34:28,620
[Lee Hyun Jun: To be able to become a couple—a match—
with a friend I like.]

1352
01:34:28,620 --> 01:34:31,830
[Lee Hyun Jun: I thought we should get along well.]

1353
01:34:31,830 --> 01:34:36,770
[Kim Sun Wook: When we became a couple, I was really happy.]

1354
01:34:36,770 --> 01:34:40,770
[Kim Sun Wook: That this person's final choice is me—
that his final conclusion is me.]

1355
01:34:40,770 --> 01:34:44,570
[Kim Sun Wook: But this is not the end but the start.]

1356
01:34:44,570 --> 01:34:49,440
[Kim Sun Wook: It's different out there
as compared to being in here.]

1357
01:34:49,440 --> 01:34:51,310
[Kim Sun Wook: So, we need to adjust to each other.]

1358
01:34:51,310 --> 01:34:54,250
[Kim Sun Wook: I thought about things more realistically.]

1359
01:34:54,980 --> 01:34:58,190
[Kim Sun Wook: I think we'll get along well.]

1360
01:34:59,120 --> 01:35:03,790
[Kim Sun Wook: We will overcome it bickering with each other.]

1361
01:35:03,860 --> 01:35:05,620
[Shy]

1362
01:35:05,660 --> 01:35:07,460
[Kim Sun Wook: Let's take photos together.]

1363
01:35:08,660 --> 01:35:11,270
[Making memories together]

1364
01:35:08,660 --> 01:35:09,380
Like this.

1365
01:35:09,380 --> 01:35:10,140
It's going to break.

1366
01:35:10,140 --> 01:35:10,800
Be careful.

1367
01:35:11,670 --> 01:35:14,070
[Lee Hyun Jun: Not bad, right?]
[Kim Sun Wook: You look good on camera.]

1368
01:35:14,070 --> 01:35:15,140
[Lee Hyun Jun: You too.]

1369
01:35:15,340 --> 01:35:17,810
[Kim Sun Wook: But I can feel it too.]
[Lee Hyun Jun: What?]

1370
01:35:17,810 --> 01:35:19,940
[Kim Sun Wook: That you think of me positively.]

1371
01:35:20,880 --> 01:35:24,280
[Lee Hyun Jun: Oh, so you felt it.]

1372
01:35:24,280 --> 01:35:27,620
[Lee Hyun Jun: I thought you didn't feel it.]
[Kim Sun Wook: I can feel it all.]

1373
01:35:28,020 --> 01:35:29,820
[Kim Sun Wook: Smile.]

1374
01:35:32,490 --> 01:35:34,820
[Lee Hyun Jun: 1, 2, 3!]

1375
01:35:38,360 --> 01:35:42,300
[Lee Hyun Jun: Say something before you take it.]
[Kim Sun Wook: Okay, I'll tell you next time.]

1376
01:35:42,900 --> 01:35:47,300
[I hope you can be happy together
every moment...]

1377
01:35:49,970 --> 01:35:53,710
[Many people are enjoying happy moments]

1378
01:35:53,980 --> 01:35:56,850
[Among them, the person waiting for
the last man is?]

1379
01:36:13,660 --> 01:36:16,400
[Lee Hyeong Jun: I chose Min Seong.]

1380
01:36:21,470 --> 01:36:25,810
[Oh Min Seong]
[Lee Hyeong Jun: Because I like Min Seong. So I chose him.]

1381
01:36:27,080 --> 01:36:29,940
[Lee Hyeong Jun: What should I say to Min Seong?]

1382
01:36:29,940 --> 01:36:32,480
[Lee Hyeong Jun: I've been thinking about it.]

1383
01:36:34,150 --> 01:36:38,890
[Lee Hyeong Jun: So before I came here, in the car,]

1384
01:36:38,890 --> 01:36:42,360
[Lee Hyeong Jun: I used my phone to jot down what I should say.]

1385
01:36:42,360 --> 01:36:45,290
[Lee Hyeong Jun: I thought a lot too.]

1386
01:36:46,830 --> 01:36:49,360
[Oh Min Seong: My final choice's got to be Hyeong Jun.]

1387
01:36:49,360 --> 01:36:52,970
[Oh Min Seong: Because I like him.
Who else should I choose?]

1388
01:36:52,970 --> 01:36:54,440
[Oh Min Seong: Of course I should choose the person I like.]

1389
01:36:54,770 --> 01:36:59,640
[Walking towards Hyeong Jun without any concerns]

1390
01:37:06,780 --> 01:37:09,050
[Oh Min Seong: I just think it's good. Everything is good.]

1391
01:37:09,050 --> 01:37:11,850
[Oh Min Seong: So he chose me. That's what I thought.]

1392
01:37:12,990 --> 01:37:16,660
[Oh Min Seong: I don't know either. It was an interesting feeling.]

1393
01:37:16,660 --> 01:37:18,790
[Oh Min Seong: But it's a good feeling.]

1394
01:37:19,130 --> 01:37:21,930
[Oh Min Seong: It's a good feeling.]

1395
01:37:21,930 --> 01:37:24,500
[Oh Min Seong: It's great.]

1396
01:37:26,870 --> 01:37:32,010
[Lee Hyeong Jun: I thought he would come.
I was happy to see him coming.]

1397
01:37:32,010 --> 01:37:36,280
[Lee Hyeong Jun: Mm... I was really happy.]

1398
01:37:40,750 --> 01:37:43,490
[Lee Hyeong Jun: I missed you so much.]

1399
01:37:44,150 --> 01:37:47,760
[Oh Min Seong: I missed you so much.]
[Lee Hyeong Jun: Quite a lot?]

1400
01:37:48,820 --> 01:37:54,300
[Lee Hyeong Jun: Why are you dressed so thinly?]
[Oh Min Seong: I have to look cool.]

1401
01:37:54,300 --> 01:38:00,100
[Lee Hyeong Jun: I missed him a lot,
so I couldn't help but hug him.]

1402
01:38:00,500 --> 01:38:02,840
[Oh Min Seong: I thought my heart stopped beating.]

1403
01:38:02,840 --> 01:38:05,510
[Oh Min Seong: His actions like this are so cute.]

1404
01:38:06,740 --> 01:38:10,710
[Oh Min Seong: How could this be? Don't you think he's cute?]

1405
01:38:11,180 --> 01:38:16,580
[Oh Min Seong: Don't you think he's cute doing things like that?
He doesn't seem like someone who'd do something like that.]

1406
01:38:17,190 --> 01:38:19,590
[Oh Min Seong: Your hands are so cold.]
[Lee Hyeong Jun: I've been waiting for a long time.]

1407
01:38:19,590 --> 01:38:21,460
[Oh Min Seong: Really?]
[Lee Hyeong Jun: Yeah.]

1408
01:38:22,320 --> 01:38:25,590
[Oh Min Seong: Your hands are too cold.]

1409
01:38:26,930 --> 01:38:33,130
[Lee Hyeong Jun: Do you like me a lot?]
[Oh Min Seong: Of course.]

1410
01:38:33,130 --> 01:38:37,270
